{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"auto"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The scanner chooses live or single-shot mode based on the source of the image. An image constructed with RawImageLoadOptions.liveSource equal to true will be processed in live mode, otherwise it will be processed in single-shot mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"On Android liveSource is automatically set to true if the ImageRef is created from Nv21 image data."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"On iOS liveSource is automatically set to true if the ImageRef is created from a CMSampleBuffer."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKProcessingMode\/auto","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKProcessingMode"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkprocessingmode\/auto"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkprocessingmode\/auto"]}],"metadata":{"title":"SBSDKProcessingMode.auto","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKProcessingModeAuto"}],"symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Case","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@E@SBSDKProcessingMode@SBSDKProcessingModeAuto","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"auto"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}]},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKProcessingMode/auto":{"abstract":[{"text":"The scanner chooses live or single-shot mode based on the source of the image. An image constr